title: Strömsbergs IF
text:
Strömsbergs IF is a <a href="Sweden">Swedish</a> <a href="association%20Football">football</a> club located in <a href="Tierp">Tierp</a> in <a href="Uppsala%20County">Uppsala County</a>.
Background.
Since their foundation Strömsbergs IF has participated mainly in the middle and lower divisions of the <a href="Swedish%20football%20league%20system">Swedish football league system</a>. Following promotion at the end of the 2009 season, the club currently plays in Division 2 Norrland which is the fourth tier of Swedish football. They play their home matches at the Strömbergs IP, Heden in Tierp.
Strömsbergs IF are affiliated to the <a href="Upplands%20Fotbollf%C3%B6rbund">Upplands Fotbollförbund</a>.
